                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="experience-card">
              <div
                class="experience-image"
                style="background-image:url('/images/fassia/pool-evening.jpg');"
              ></div>
              <div class="experience-overlay"></div>
              <div class="experience-inner">
                <div class="experience-tag">Pool & Outdoor</div>
                <h3 class="experience-title">Afternoons by the water</h3>
                <p class="experience-text">
                  A calm outdoor pool and terrace area for a quick swim, a relaxed break or
                  small private gatherings.
                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="experience-card">
              <div
                class="experience-image"
                style="background-image:url('/images/fassia/conference-dinner.jpg');"
